{"tid":966372,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"[緊急求絲打指引人生]做唔做依份工?","createTime":"2019-01-02T17:49:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-05T20:27:25.000Z","uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"eb3848917fb5eb7984d572173ac57a56e2b981eb","tid":966372,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:49:35.000Z","msg":"依家個心情好似水行俠咁好想有個女性教佢點做好<br />\n<br />\n個人背景:今年25歲,單身,經濟仲算支持到搵多陣工。<br />\n學歷:ive電機hd畢業(rmit pt degree讀左一個學期quit左),畢業做左大工程公司年半(intern to 助理工程師),之後轉過幾間小,中工程公司(試用期前自己冇做),之後做過sales賣波鞋,而家依份in左係酒店保安,而家番9小時,要輪姦通宵,都有~14k. 轉得太多工,都唔知好唔好做長工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n人生冇方向<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"222ab161501cf098c5339614c45f9ae31c64bde1","tid":966372,"uid":9624,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T17:57:17.000Z","msg":"覺得你應該真心諗下自己想做咩先<br />\n見你跳黎跳去突然間又賣波鞋咁<br />\n如果你而家貿貿然為搵而搵一份長工<br />\n分分鐘又係做兩做又唔想撈又走又搵無限loop<br />\n<br />\n唔好介意咩人工咩工時<br />\n去搵自己興趣 工作先會無咁難捱"},{"pid":"28eface5c76c74a1ccf309d5936e17bd5d8fec19","tid":966372,"uid":90820,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T18:00:13.000Z","msg":"點解要搵絲打答<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b0f85603bd6787f4a394ea4ffdd289a90d22bb","tid":966372,"uid":176471,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T18:03:50.000Z","msg":"做做下工程撚 有咩睇唔開做保安<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bc64d5a254ff0