又唔想撈又走又搵無限loop<br />\n<br />\n唔好介意咩人工咩工時<br />\n去搵自己興趣 工作先會無咁難捱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T20:55:50.000Z","msg":"依家我係試工期,有一個禮拜學下野,可以比我諗做唔做<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 絲打其實我真係諗左幾年(廢左幾年),自己究竟有咩興趣?有咩叻?但真係諗唔到😂晝畫,差。音樂,白痴。數學,大學工程數已死。語言,最多識聽少少日文,但英文又好一般。。<br />\n樣樣野都係勉強識d,點先可以搵到啱自己興趣&amp;工作<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 以前做野冇咩成功感&amp;興趣，一味勉強自己,個心好灰。。。。我怕我可能有情緒病<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf4c8027c4e046a716b1c761b18e47f9460c1037","tid":966372,"uid":194687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T23:21:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5671a6d1a0cdcb01c6049c7078af69e5c6fcfb51","tid":966372,"uid":176471,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5cfba5b7e9490bf274f7ad45b0d1f6ec8da1d308","tid":966372,"uid":140357,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"91b0f85603bd6787f4a394ea4ffdd289a90d22bb","tid":966372,"uid":176471,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T18:03:50.000Z","msg":"做做下工程撚 有咩睇唔開做保安<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-02T20:41:09.000Z","msg":"做工程根本係俾d師傅&amp;物料玩死<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n考左個牌咪試下做<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T17:39:32.000Z","msg":"25歲真係要保安？<br />\n要巡樓架喎 每日行幾十層你確定真係得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n考到個牌 仲後生其實可以試下做cs"},{"pid":"f989995d57d2f2a5f1441b47751b0565ef1f1f36","tid":966372,"uid":97604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T18:23:39.000Z","msg":"FF 少陣先<br />\n除非你有水行俠噉man，但我諗你有都唔洗喺度FF<br />\n<br />\n你要知前途係點，唔該你學上面啲巴打講，諗清楚自己想點<br />\n然後搵啲有閱歷有經驗嘅人傾，唔係淨係搵女同你傾<br /